    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-7 bento-card p-10 bg-amber-50 border-amber-200 flex flex-col justify-between group">
        <div>
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mb-8 border border-amber-100">ğŸº</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 italic text-[#2D2D2D]">Brouwerij De Kobold</h2>
          <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">Ambachtelijke stadsbrouwerij. Samen hebben we mede gemaakt van de honing van Rogers bijenvolken.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.brouwerijdekobold.nl" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest bg-white/50 w-fit px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-amber-200 hover:bg-[#FFB400] transition-all">Bezoek website â†—</a>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-5 bento-card p-10 bg-green-50 border-green-200 flex flex-col justify-between group">
        <div>
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm mb-8 border border-green-100">ğŸŒ³</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 italic text-[#2D2D2D]">Voedselbos Werelds</h2>
          <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] leading-relaxed mb-6">Een circulair bos in de Kop van Malden. De vaste standplaats voor onze gemonitorde bijenkasten.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.voedselboswerelds.nl" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest bg-white/50 w-fit px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-green-200 hover:bg-[#2D2D2D] hover:text-white transition-all">Ontdek het bos â†—</a>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-12 bento-card p-10 bg-[#FFB400] text-[#2D2D2D] shadow-xl">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 italic">HackNature.org</h2>
            <p class="text-lg font-medium mb-8">Monitoring van CO2, temperatuur, humiditeit en gewicht. Technologie die het bijenvolk ontziet.</p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-[9px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">
                <div class="bg-black/10 p-3 rounded-xl border border-black/10">ğŸŒ¡ï¸ Sensor Data</div>
                <div class="bg-black/10 p-3 rounded-xl border border-black/10">ğŸ¤– Maker Tech</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-black/5 rounded-[2rem] p-8 border border-black/10 italic font-medium text-center">
            <p>"Bijen dragen actief bij aan het herstel van insect-bestoven planten in Malden."</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Educatieve Link -->
    <div class="mb-20 p-8 bg-stone-50 rounded-[3rem] border border-stone-200 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
